<p>How in facebook log in API, get name, user name &amp; email in cordova facebook app</p>  <p><strong>how find what the response object look like</strong> in JSON (public_profile IS FOR GETTING ALL ABOVE INFO) :</p>  <p>FROM  <a href="https://github.com/Wizcorp/phonegap-facebook-plugin/" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/Wizcorp/phonegap-facebook-plugin/</a></p>  <pre><code>var fbLoginSuccess = function (userData) {     alert("UserInfo: " + JSON.stringify(userData));     facebookConnectPlugin.getAccessToken(function(token) {         alert("Token: " + token);     }, function(err) {         alert("Could not get access token: " + err);     }); }  facebookConnectPlugin.login(["public_profile"],     fbLoginSuccess,     function (error) { alert("" + error) } ); </code></pre>